sentences: Christian Walz (born 4 September 1978, Stockholm) is a Swedish artist, songwriter, and producer.
He released his self-titled debut album in 1999, aged 20.
It took five years for the next album to be released.
"Paint By Numbers" was released in May 2004, became a Swedish Grammy winner and a big hit.
His third album, "The Corner", was released on 26 November 2008 in Sweden.
